Package: GeoInno
Type: Package
Title: Calculation of types of complexity and aggregated indices at the level of spatial units
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Broekel
Maintainer: The package maintainer <tobroworks@icloud.com>
Description: The package features functions to work with patent data in the context of the Geography of Innovation literature. At this stage, it calculates indices approximating technological complexity using patent data.
    It also contains functions of aggregating these indices at the level of spatial units.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    igraph,
    tidyverse,
    widyr,
    netdist,
    Rdpack,
    magrittr,
    R (>= 2.10)
RdMacros: Rdpack
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
